    "data": [
        {
            "title": "【新盤直擊】啟德海灣第2期加推118伙｜折實均呎21,932元 低首批約8.19%｜同柱戶加幅最高4.66%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由嘉華國際、會德豐地產及中國海外合作發展的啟德海灣第2期，於上周六（18日）首輪公開發售160伙，售出131伙後，發展商隨即公布第2號價單，加推118伙。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新一批單位折實均呎為21,932元。若與本月9日公布的首張價單折實均呎23,888元比較，新一批單位低約8.19%，單位折實入場價為560.8萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今批單位全數來自1C座，主要為景觀相對受限的單位，亦未包括首張價單所涵蓋、景觀較佳的1A座及1B座三房戶，因此拉低整批單位的折實均呎。不過，若按同座同柱單位比較，實際加幅介乎2.93%至4.66%，顯示今批單位定價與首張價單大致相若。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5b343e82-15b0-3fe5-8d2e-507209d4fd24-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"啟德海灣第2期價單\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:啟德海灣第2期價單;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4moWoXk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">啟德海灣第2期價單</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【新盤動向】啟德海灣第2期周六首輪售160伙 折實均呎約20,683元｜周日招標售65伙\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【新盤動向】啟德海灣第2期周六首輪售160伙 折實均呎約20,683元｜周日招標售65伙;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4eCNAuK\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【新盤動向】啟德海灣第2期周六首輪售160伙 折實均呎約20,683元｜周日招標售65伙</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"啟德海灣2期首輪沽逾8成｜柏傲莊III首輪88伙全數售罄｜十大屋苑交投回升 麗城三房升值逾3倍\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:啟德海灣2期首輪沽逾8成｜柏傲莊III首輪88伙全數售罄｜十大屋苑交投回升 麗城三房升值逾3倍;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3QxZbRU\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">啟德海灣2期首輪沽逾8成｜柏傲莊III首輪88伙全數售罄｜十大屋苑交投回升 麗城三房升值逾3倍</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>啟德海灣第2期加推118伙 折實均呎約21,932元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">啟德海灣第2期周六（18日）公布第2號價單，加推118伙，包括79伙一房戶及39伙兩房戶，實用面積介乎278至613平方呎。整批單位以定價計算市值約12.2億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">發展商維持最高25%折扣優惠，今批單位折實售價由約560.8萬至1,439.8萬元，折實呎價介乎約18,454至28,006元，折實均呎為21,932元，較首張價單的23,888元低約8.19%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今批單位雖以1C座單位為主，亦包括部分高層戶，但由於未有涵蓋首張價單中的1A座及1B座三房戶，整體景觀及戶型分布與首批不同，令折實均呎低於首張價單。若以同座同柱單位比較，售價則錄得輕微上調。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>一房折實入場價約560.8萬元 </strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第2號價單中，一房入場單位為第1C座5樓N室，實用面積278平方呎，折實售價約560.8萬元，折實呎價約20,172元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wc9eNKh3r6awQ5OzFa54DQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/b81ffe69ac5b5d2fccee784792094919\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>一房入場單位：第1C座5樓N室平面圖</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>兩房折實入場價約786.2萬元 </strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兩房入場單位為第1C座5樓K室，實用面積426平方呎，折實售價約786.2萬元，折實呎價約18,454元，亦為整批單位中折實呎價最低的一伙。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Hfq9X1HOOqNlCQt8RZbh.w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/6c41d876c72395ef4bac8c865627a67f\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>兩房入場單位：第1C座5樓K室</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">整批單位中，折實呎價最高的單位為第1C座35樓N室，屬一房戶，實用面積278平方呎，折實售價約778.6萬元，折實呎價約28,006元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>同座同柱比較 實際加幅約2.93%至4.66%</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第2號價單折實均呎雖較首張價單低約8.19%，但若以同座同柱單位逐一對比，實際加幅介乎2.93%至4.66%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以第2號價單的第1C座18樓M室為例，折實呎價為20,951元；首張價單同柱的17樓M室折實呎價則為20,017元，兩者相差約4.66%。若考慮樓層差異，兩張價單的定價基本相若。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/D1CsY.C1gPS7pB8wScv6Ng--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/4ec8d9bab2ba8ae65e7dee4342722f14\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>項目背景</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">啟德海灣第2期位於啟德承豐道15號，合共提供1121伙，實用面積由258至771平方呎，涵蓋開放式至三房戶。小學校網為34校網。中學校網為九龍城區。項目的預計關鍵日期為2026年6月30日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"啟德海灣\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:啟德海灣;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/啟德海灣-28390\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">啟德海灣</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"柏傲莊\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:柏傲莊;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/柏傲莊-27180\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">柏傲莊</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"九龍城\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:九龍城;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/九龍城-27371\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">九龍城</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"啟德\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:啟德;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/啟德-27394\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">啟德</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"新聞連結\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%A4%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A-%E5%95%9F%E5%BE%B7%E6%B5%B7%E7%81%A3%E7%AC%AC2%E6%9C%9F%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A8118%E4%BC%99-%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6%E5%9D%87%E5%91%8E21-932%E5%85%83-%E4%BD%8E%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E7%B4%848-19-%E5%90%8C%E6%9F%B1%E6%88%B6%E5%8A%A0%E5%B9%85%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%984-66-75621\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"28Hse App\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse App;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/appdownload\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse App</a>。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%A4%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A-%E5%95%9F%E5%BE%B7%E6%B5%B7%E7%81%A3%E7%AC%AC2%E6%9C%9F%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A8118%E4%BC%99-%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6%E5%9D%87%E5%91%8E21-932%E5%85%83-%E4%BD%8E%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E7%B4%848-101817420.html",
