        {
            "title": "今日英股:中東緊張局勢升溫及油價反彈拖累股市下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xr0EPFwqixEcasgsuW1OCQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEB7O0CS_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 英國股市週一開盤走低,美國與伊朗之間的緊張局勢升級令投資者情緒受挫。美國在<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>附近扣押一艘懸掛伊朗國旗的船隻,引發市場對全球能源供應進一步中斷的擔憂,並使外交努力受挫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間03:13(格林威治標準時間07:13),藍籌股指數FTSE 100下跌0.4%,扭轉了上週0.7%的漲幅,而英國GBP/USD下跌0.04%至1.3512。DAX下跌1.1%,CAC 40下跌1%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-670fe8ee-5ecf-3c59-ade4-1a0a5c8fd712-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">避險情緒加劇,此前唐納德·特朗普在Truth Social上發文稱伊朗違反了停火協議,並警告如果德黑蘭拒絕提議的協議,華盛頓可能升級軍事行動。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普補充說,美國已經\"接管\"了這艘船隻,並威脅如果緊張局勢惡化,將針對伊朗的關鍵基礎設施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗官員回應稱可能進行報復,軍方當局警告稱扣押船隻將被視為違反停火協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">官方媒體還表示,除非美國解除海上封鎖,否則德黑蘭可能跳過即將在伊斯蘭堡舉行的談判,這突顯出雙方在制裁、鈾儲備和對這一戰略水道的控制方面存在日益擴大的分歧。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著市場對霍爾木茲海峽航運中斷的擔憂重新浮現,油價大幅反彈,給股市帶來壓力,並加劇了通脹擔憂。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>英國市場綜述</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>M&amp;C Saatchi</strong>報告稱,2025年同類營運利潤下降26.1%,並取消了末期股息,轉而進行股份回購。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司警告稱,預計中東衝突將對其2026年的體育和娛樂業務產生重大影響,加上消費者狀況疲軟和地緣政治不確定性帶來的壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Plus500</strong>報告了五年多來最強勁的季度表現,得益於美國市場的快速增長、客戶增加,以及儘管面臨交易阻力仍保持穩健的盈利能力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Mulberry Group</strong>實現了2026財年的強勁轉機,年增長率達5.7%,受下半年所有地區和渠道的大幅反彈推動。<br/><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Evoke plc</strong>確認正在與Bally’s Intralot S.A.就潛在的每股50便士收購進行談判。擬議交易可能包括股份和現金的組合,但尚未保證達成確定要約,決定截止日期定於5月18日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Renishaw Plc</strong>上調了2026財年展望,受半導體和航空航天領域強勁需求推動,提高了收入和利潤預期。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E8%8B%B1%E8%82%A1-%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E5%8D%87%E6%BA%AB%E5%8F%8A%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88%E6%8B%96%E7%B4%AF%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-081236120.html",
