            "title": "財經｜中銀香港五一黃金周延長3分行服務時間 跨境客需求增",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜中銀香港五一黃金周延長3分行服務時間 跨境客需求增\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nvJ6N1NDpC3.YMtrx76erg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜中銀香港五一黃金周延長3分行服務時間 跨境客需求增</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中銀香港(02388)指出，將於五一黃金周延長3家指定分行服務時間，分別為銅鑼灣分行、廣東道中銀理財中心及屯門市廣場分行，以配合跨境客戶開戶及理財需要。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行個人金融及財富管理部副總經理劉賽麗指出，去年五一黃金周期間，其跨境客戶日均新開戶數目按年上升超過三成，反映不少旅客趁黃金周假期訪港順道開立銀行賬戶。隨着特區政府近年大力推動多項大型盛事，中銀香港預計今年將有更多跨境客戶於長假期間訪港，並抽空到訪分行使用銀行服務或開戶。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d82aa18d-7b7c-3e86-a65c-5cb4292c6b16-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">到訪分行前可通過網站及平台預約，3家指定分行將提供開戶、賬戶重檢及財富管理等非現金交易服務，跨境服務大使會在現場解答客戶查詢。到訪客戶有機會獲見面禮及參與理財「黃金賞」大抽獎和幸運財富賞。至於香港國際機場銀行服務中心則全年營業。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E4%B8%AD%E9%8A%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%94-%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%91%A8%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B73%E5%88%86%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E6%99%82%E9%96%93-%E8%B7%A8%E5%A2%83%E5%AE%A2%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E5%A2%9E-071054538.html",
